<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id122ecb83-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777" identifier="/us/usc/t44/s1914"><num value="1914">§ 1914.</num><heading> Implementation of depository library program by Director of the Government Publishing Office</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Director of the Government Publishing Office, with the approval of the Joint Committee on Printing, as provided by <ref href="/us/usc/t44/s103">section 103 of this title</ref>, may use any measures he considers necessary for the economical and practical implementation of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id122ecb84-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/620">Pub. L. 90–620</ref>, <date date="1968-10-22">Oct. 22, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/82/1287">82 Stat. 1287</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/113/235/dH/tI/s1301/c">Pub. L. 113–235, div. H, title I, § 1301(c)</ref>, <date date="2014-12-16">Dec. 16, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/2537">128 Stat. 2537</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
